Package: MRManalyzeR
Type: Package
Title: Process and Analyse Targeted LC-MS Lipidomics & Metabolomics Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "J Smith",
                  email = "mattyjsmith123@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: End-to-end processing pipeline for targeted lipidomics and
    metabolomics data exported from Waters TargetLynx. Reads xlsx workbooks,
    builds a peak-area / concentration matrix with optional SNR filtering,
    blank filtering, missing-value imputation, normalisation, concentration
    adjustment, and batch correction, then renders self-contained HTML data
    quality and statistical reports. Driven from a single YAML config via
    `run_MRManalyzeR()`.
